de.ovgu.featureide.fm.core.base

Interface IFeatureStructure

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    FeatureStructure

    public interface IFeatureStructure
    Manages all structural information of a feature.
    Intended for tree structures (features are represented by tree nodes).
    Author:
    Sebastian Krieter, Marcus Pinnecke
